metadata.name: Dreams of a mermaid #1/10
metadata.description: What does a woman dream about? Even if she is a robot she dreams about love!  And she wants to beautify herself and everything around!!! Just the robot mermaid of the future has got a superpower, like levitation: Voila!... and lilies are graciously floating in the air! But a new hat is what the true woman always needs, as it is one of the most important accessories for her image! 'Well, how do I look like?...
